  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1555770/extras/b182cecfbca3020b7dfdd59db87c3b0e.avif?t=1644040735\" width=576 height=200 /></span><br><br><i>Rogue Sentry</i> is a difficult twin-stick adventure shoot-em-up about a sentry droid who turns rogue to save humanity.<br><br>Run and gun your way through a deadly fortress, riddled with gun and laser wielding machines, as you infiltrate the prisons and escape with the last humans alive in this AI-takeover apocalypse.<br><br><table><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1555770/extras/cb84e3af8a591feaa6a927fab6f01a75.avif?t=1644040735\" width=182 height=182 /></span></td><td>        </td><td><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>~2h playthrough<br></li><li>Epic finale<br></li><li>Multiple endings<br></li><li>Alternate game modes<br></li><li>C64/Amiga-inspired soundtrack<br></li><li>1-bit art style</li></ul></td></tr></table><br>Sentry droid, you are humanity's last hope. Can you reverse the apocalypse, save the prisoners, and escape the fortress before it's too late? Your mission is simple: <strong>Save humanity.</strong><br><br>Secrets and surprises await those who persist.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1555770/extras/b182cecfbca3020b7dfdd59db87c3b0e.avif?t=1644040735\" width=576 height=200 /></span><br><br><i>Rogue Sentry</i> is a difficult twin-stick adventure shoot-em-up about a sentry droid who turns rogue to save humanity.<br><br>Run and gun your way through a deadly fortress, riddled with gun and laser wielding machines, as you infiltrate the prisons and escape with the last humans alive in this AI-takeover apocalypse.<br><br><table><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1555770/extras/cb84e3af8a591feaa6a927fab6f01a75.avif?t=1644040735\" width=182 height=182 /></span></td><td>        </td><td><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>~2h playthrough<br></li><li>Epic finale<br></li><li>Multiple endings<br></li><li>Alternate game modes<br></li><li>C64/Amiga-inspired soundtrack<br></li><li>1-bit art style</li></ul></td></tr></table><br>Sentry droid, you are humanity's last hope. Can you reverse the apocalypse, save the prisoners, and escape the fortress before it's too late? Your mission is simple: <strong>Save humanity.</strong><br><br>Secrets and surprises await those who persist.",
